front.title: •Sienar Fleet Systems
front.gametext: Deploy on Wakeelmui system. Retrieve 1 Force each time you deploy a TIE. Also, once per turn you may relocate a TIE just lost from table to Used Pile. (Immune to Alter while you occupy Wakeelmui.)
front.lore: Industry leader in fighter production, but produces several other products. Constantly working on advancements o the baseline TIE design.

combo: Sienar Fleet Systems + Commander Brandei + Dreaded Imperial Starfleet + TIE's with matching pilots.
